

Android Application name :- HUNGRY TUMMY 
Submitted by :- Desai Nileshwari S. 
Android Project Synopsis :
	Mumbai is a city of dreams. People come to this city to achieve something big in their life, and mostly it comprises of students. Young minds step foot away from their home and the first problem they face is food. Home food is missed and studying/ working late nights adds up to it. So I, as a beginner with android platform, have developed an application which helps to order food online and get home delivery. There are many places which stays open all night round but it is not feasible to go out to the joint at 1am in the night. I have tried developing this application which provides information according to the area you stay in; about which restaurants are open near you at that hour of time, and from where you can fill your tummy.  I have tried to make it simple by allowing the user to select their area ie. Western line, central line, harbor line and according to that a list of restaurants will be displayed with their address and phone number. So that the person can call, order and avoid sleeping hungry.
