Layout for the next page:

 

Selecting one of the three options would display the list of restaurants open at that instant of time and who would deliver at your door step.

Conclusion

	This application is helpful to easily view the food joints accessible at any hour and get a home delivery. This application is not only helpful to the students but every person who feels a need to order when hungry. 


